<br>
Using /assist <br>
<br>
You hit /pet attack<br>
<br>
Nothing happens. . .<br>
<br>
Because the point at which you hit the /assist the puller had switched targets to con some other mob, not the one incoming.<br>
<br>
The very next thing you need to hit is the /pet back off, /pet as you were.  You want to clear the aggro of the pet from that target.<br>
If you don't, the pet will still have that target on the hate list, and it will run to attack it as soon as the mob comes within range of you.  Can get very ugly if your pet suddenly takes off out the door, down the hall, etc. to go attack that mob.<br>
